title: Metro Station - Charles de Gaulle - Etoile
description:
Serves Lines 1, 6 and 2 and RER Line A. 
If you want to get to the Arc de Triomphe, get off at this stop. once off the train, follow the signs for the Arc de Triomphe (it will be in white letters in a brown rectangle). You will see the arc in front of you as you leave the station to the surface.
